EXPRESSION:
CASE
    WHEN COALESCE(VLCS_VSB_COLLATERAL.AS_OF_DT, ' ') <> ' ' THEN to_date(VLCS_VSB_COLLATERAL.AS_OF_DT, 'yyyy-MM-dd')
    ELSE NULL
  END AS AS_OF_DT
CASE WHEN COALESCE(VLCS_VSB_COLLATERAL.APPRAISAL_DT,' ') <>' 'THEN  to_date(VLCS_VSB_COLLATERAL.APPRAISAL_DT , 'yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE NULL END AS APPRAISAL_DT
